{"tid":1967523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚德塞快看！非裔被中国指控成病毒來源 黑人慘遭種族歧視","createTime":"2020-04-11T04:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T00:58:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"379e295140ce73cfad86038ec36186070d5deba9","tid":1967523,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"中國廣州的武漢肺炎疫情持續延燒，4月持續出現本土病例，中國當局將矛頭指向當地非洲人，認為他們是病毒感染源，要求他們離開租屋處或酒店，甚至禁止他們進入公共場所，導致非洲人流落街頭。<br />\n<br />\n《撒哈拉報導者》（Sahara Reporters）報導，在中國的非洲人證實被下逐客令的消息，當地政府正在用武力將外國人趕出自己的家園。在中國的非洲人說，「有人聲稱，黑人是現在正向中國輸入武漢肺炎的人。當地目前不允許外國人，特別是黑人進入公共場所，包括購物中心、飯店和醫院。他們被房東驅逐，被飯店趕出來，只因為武漢肺炎，讓他們經歷各種各樣的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n為了平息逐客令，廣州非洲社區領導人與政府舉行了一次會議，儘管會議作出了決議並取得了實際成果，但非洲人認為逐客令仍未結束。一名受到影響的非洲人表示，還不能說逐客令已經結束，現在仍有非洲人流落街頭，在雨天無處可去。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府在給受到影響省市的外國人的通知中指出，「從4月5日至4月7日，街道將組織轄區內非洲籍承租客到指定地點（居委會前面的空地）進行核酸篩查，要求業主／居民知悉並通知家人。」<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，在中國微博上黑人成病毒來源成為熱門話題，並出現大量種族歧視的言論，「黑人就是最低等的人，好吃懶做犯罪率高」、「建議權世界清剿黑人」、「我以前還一直在享有的國家為什麼歧視黑人，現在是明白了」、「就是看不起黑人，他們就是最劣等的人」。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，引發許多非裔網友不滿，在推特紛紛標籤「#ChinaLiedAndPeopleDied」（中國說謊、人民去死）、「#ChinaMustExplain」（中國必須解釋），在非洲國家引發熱烈迴響，甚至在奈及利亞，也是排行榜上的熱門標籤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3130241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3130241&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=4238cba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3130241&h=705f2dbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3130241</a>"},{"pid":"899ba5847e7bbad821957c7fc54c1a91e9743e87","tid":1967523,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:14:25.000Z","msg":"唔知，唔見，我無留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6f679aa8c1758ac851905640e9ce2f2bf4c738","tid":1967523,"uid":37666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"呢隻賣國狗點會留意"},{"pid":"10996ee2e3f0deb33e55c08d346d5f715e9ba672","tid":1967523,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3307bdb61bdd3bede16c7a2130e641e67b2bd458","tid":1967523,"uid":278697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"鹹濕菜，一坨屎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4ec1300edb0be7c1e942ef500a1863bd7a153f","tid":1967523,"uid":202051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"用歧視嚴重嗰抨擊其他國家啲未經歷過終国歧視<br />\n兩舊都係屎黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同省可以互相歧視<br />\n同一個省城市歧視鄉村人<br />\n唯一就係唔會有人歧視美國佬因為潛意識覺得鬼佬高級啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccfa826f721927048b171c4181e68fbde1b8453","tid":1967523,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:36:00.000Z","msg":"黑奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50233f246fe81943003ccb7e6a710fb62b146ad3","tid":1967523,"uid":269515,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyceFnF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyceFnF.jpg&h=3d821449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zV6V9f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzV6V9f0.jpg&h=91c4b388&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e50645e9e29be270ddaac25718d4464464e14b55","tid":1967523,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim